Package hu.bme.mit.theta.cat.dsl.gen

Class CatBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.cat.dsl.gen.CatBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CatListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class CatBaseListener extends Object implements CatListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CatListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
